<div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>2. Jean Renoir (41 votes)</p></div>

<div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>3. Ingmar Bergman (37 votes)</p></div>

<div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>4. Luis Bufiuel (33 votes)</p></div>

<div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>5. Sergei Eisenstein (29 votes)</p></div>

<div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>=6. John Ford, Jean-Luc Godard (28 votes each)</p></div>

<div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>8. Buster Keaton (25 votes)</p></div>

<div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>9. Federico Fellini (23 votes)</p></div>

